*xfdesktop-4.12.2 (17 May 2015)

  17 May 2015; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> +xfdesktop-4.12.2.ebuild:
  Version bump with some bugfixes.

  01 Apr 2015; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org>
  +files/xfdesktop-4.12.1-no-thunar-build.patch, xfdesktop-4.12.1.ebuild:
  Fix build failure with USE=-thunar, bug #544260.

*xfdesktop-4.12.1 (22 Mar 2015)

  22 Mar 2015; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> +xfdesktop-4.12.1.ebuild:
  Version bump with bugfixes. Add slot operators to deps.

