*xfdesktop-4.11.6 (07 Apr 2014)

  07 Apr 2014; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org> +xfdesktop-4.11.6.ebuild:
  Version bump.

  06 Apr 2014; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org> -xfdesktop-4.11.4.ebuild:
  old

  06 Apr 2014; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org> xfdesktop-4.11.5.ebuild:
  Enable USE="thunar" by default because since >= 4.11 the sys-apps/dbus (and
  dev-libs/dbus-glib) dependencies are no longer optional anyway which was the
  reason for not enabling it for 4.10.

